properties.HYPERLANES: Perlemian Trade Route, Corellian Run, Koros Trunk Line, Shawken Spur, Namadii Corridor
properties.PLACEMENT_SOURCES: Essential Atlas, TFA RPG Beginner Game
properties.INTERESTING: capital of governments; nicknamed "Queen of the Core" or "City of Spires", also variously known as Republic Center and Imperial Center; 5,127 city levels built up from the crust by time of CW, divided into megablocks, blocks and subblocks; planet divided into blocks, which were divided into zones; once mostly covered in oceans, later drained; artificial Western Sea was tourist hotspot

properties.PLACEMENT_SOURCES: Essential Atlas, TFA RPG Beginner Game
properties.INTERESTING: high-pressure methane atmosphere; discovered before Republic's formation; ecumenopolis comparable in population and scale to Coruscant, but lacked its charm, aesthetics; some examples of planet's ecosystem were preserved (vast fields of sprawling vines); HQ of Techno Union, which joined CIS under Wat Tambor; Skako was then expelled from Republic; home to Octuparras
